GENERAL MOTORS ACCEPTANCE CORPORATION, a Corp., Claimant of One Buick 1926 Sedan Automobile, Engine No. 1—614—477, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. GENERAL MOTORS ACCEPTANCE CORPORATION, a Corp., Claimant of One Chevrolet Coupe Automobile, Eng. No. 3—337—243, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. GENERAL MOTORS ACCEPTANCE CORPORATION, a Corp., Claimant of One Buick Roadster Automobile, Eng. No. 1—490—479, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 6857. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. May 31, 1932.

Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Circuit Judges, and NETERER, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for the respective parties, ordered appeals in above cause dismissed; mandates forthwith.
